{"lemma":"عُقْبَى","slug":"عُقْبَى","root":"ع.ق.ب","root_slug":"ع-ق-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ق-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عُقْبَى","root":"عقب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":6},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n29840"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8F%D9%82%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%89"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n29840","headword_ar":"عُقْبَى","root":"Eqb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqibN","text_ar":"عَقِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", second quarter, in four places. ―         -b2-  It occurs in a trad. respecting the prayer of fear; in which it is said of that prayer,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAnato","text_ar":"كَانَتْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqobaY","text_ar":"عُقْبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was an affair of turns"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning that it was performed by one company after another; several companies performing it successively, by turns. (TA. [Compare"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqobapN","text_ar":"عُقْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as expl. in the third sentence of the paragraph on that word.]) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mrjE","text_ar":"مرجع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marojiEN","text_ar":"مَرْجِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A returning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"requital,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recompence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of an affair, or action. (S, O, K.) ―         -b5-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqobapN","text_ar":"عُقْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", latter half, in two places."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}